Bashir Ahmad, the Personal Assistant to the President Muhammadu Buhari on Digital and New Media, has disclosed that some unpatriotic people are waiting for Buhari to leave the presidential seat before causing mayhem in the country. The presidential aide revealed this on Sunday in a Twitter post, stating those people are still angry with Buhari for ot allowing miscreants with help of misguided outsiders to destroy Nigeria. However, Ahmad gave them a warning, expressing that whoever takes over from Buhari will also never allow them to terrorize the country. PDP Victory In FCT Council Polls, Good Omen -Ayu PDP Chieftain Clears Air On Controversies Trailing Ekiti Law… He tweeted, “Those unpatriotic people are still angry with Pres. @MBuhari for not allowing miscreants with help of misguided outsiders to destroy this country. “They’re like we can’t wait for 2023, they should know that whoever takes over from Baba will also NEVER allow them to terrorize us.